@startuml sequence_search
title Sequence — ADR Full-Text Search (Feature 09)

actor User
participant "SearchBar" as Search
participant "SearchResultsList" as Results
participant "SearchClientService" as Client
participant "SearchController" as Controller
participant "TenantContext" as Tenant
participant "SearchService" as Service
participant "CouchbaseFtsClient" as FTS
database "Couchbase FTS\n(tenant-scoped index)" as CB

== User Types Search Query ==

User -> Search : Types "event-driven" in search bar
Search -> Search : Debounce 300ms
Search -> Search : query.length >= 2?\n=> Yes, proceed

Search -> Client : search(tenantSlug, {\n  query: "event-driven",\n  status: null,\n  pageSize: 20,\n  offset: 0 })
Search -> Results : Set isLoading = true

Client -> Controller : GET /api/tenants/{slug}/search\n  ?q=event-driven\n  &pageSize=20\n  &offset=0\nAuthorization: Bearer {jwt}
Controller -> Tenant : extractTenant(jwt)
Tenant --> Controller : tenantSlug verified
Controller -> Controller : validate SearchQueryDto
Controller -> Service : search(tenantSlug, params)

== Build FTS Query ==

Service -> Service : buildFtsRequest(tenantSlug, params)
note right
  FtsSearchRequest {
    query: {
      conjunction: [
        {
          disjunction: [
            { match: "event-driven",
              field: "title",
              analyzer: "standard",
              boost: 3.0 },
            { match: "event-driven",
              field: "body",
              analyzer: "standard",
              boost: 1.0 },
            { match: "event-driven",
              field: "tags",
              analyzer: "keyword",
              boost: 2.0 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    fields: ["adrNumber", "title",
             "status", "body"],
    highlight: {
      style: "html",
      fields: ["title", "body", "tags"]
    },
    size: 20,
    from: 0,
    sort: ["-_score"]
  }
end note

== Execute FTS Query ==

Service -> FTS : execute("idx_fts_adrs_{tenantSlug}",\nftsRequest)
FTS -> CB : Search request with\nscope partition: {tenantSlug}\ncollection: adrs
CB -> CB : Full-text search across\ntitle, body, tags fields\nRanked by BM25 score
CB --> FTS : FtsSearchResponse {\n  totalHits: 8,\n  took: 12ms,\n  rows: FtsRow[] }
FTS --> Service : FtsSearchResponse

== Process Results ==

Service -> Service : mapToSearchResults(ftsRows)
loop for each FtsRow
    Service -> Service : Extract adrNumber, title,\nstatus from fields
    Service -> Service : extractSnippets(row.fragments)
    note right
      Concatenates fragment strings
      from "body" field with "..."
      separators. HTML highlight
      tags (<mark>) preserved for
      frontend rendering.
    end note
end

Service --> Controller : SearchResponse {\n  results: SearchResult[8],\n  totalHits: 8,\n  took: 12 }
Controller --> Client : 200 SearchResponse

Client --> Search : SearchResponse
Search -> Results : Set isLoading = false
Results -> Results : Render results list

Results --> User : Search results displayed:\n- ADR number + title\n- Status badge\n- Snippet with <mark>highlighted</mark> terms

== User Clicks Result ==

User -> Results : Clicks on "ADR-003"
Results -> Results : Navigate to /adrs/ADR-003

@enduml
